title: $:/plugins/tgrosinger/tw5-checklist/readme

This plugin provides a simple checklist which does not create a new tiddler for
each task. Features include:

* Check and uncheck items. Checked items move to the bottom.
* Easily update item text
* Clear all checks (re-usable lists)
* Simple, no configuration necessary

